title: Conan (the Dark Horse comics) - Complete - 50 Issues, Miniseries
description:
The first phase of the Conan comic run at Dark Horse. They stopped at issue #50, and starting fresh with Conan the Cimmerian #01 on July 16th 2008.



This torrent includes all published material in comic book format:



Conan #00 and #01-#50  -   2003 - 2008

Miniseries: Conan and the Daughters of Midora  -  2004
            Conan and the Jewels of Gwahlur  -  2005
            Conan and the Demons of Khitai  -  2005 - 2006
            Conan - Book of Thoth  -  2006
            Conan and the Songs of the Dead  -  2006
            Conan and the Midnight God  -  2007

Extras: Age of Conan - Hyborian Adventures
        Star Wars - Conan (Free Comic Book Day 2006 Special #01)


NOTE: The files are in .CBR and .CBZ file format. You will need CDisplay or a similar program to read the comics.
